Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My feelings towards Hirasaka-kun\Nwere demolished in an instant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He didn't love me at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth is he saw me as nothing\Nbut an experiment subject.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When things began to get heavy,\NRyuji Hirasaka vanished.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The hospital, wanting to\Nmaintain its own honor,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sealed the whole case, thus\Ndrawing a conclusion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I, who had a miscarriage,\Ncould've cared less.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body was craving for stimulus, and\Nin my heart ambition was sprouting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:17:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used the results of the training I\Nreceived from Ryuji Hirasaka as a weapon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Men thus gave me money and social status.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ten years later, I was still racing as\Nfast as I could, heading for the top.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the truth is, this could be\Nmy true nature, for all I know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps Hirasaka-kun saw through that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course during that time, not for one\Nmoment did I forget about him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the one who betrayed me, Ryuji Hirasaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's absurd that things have\Nturned out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stop this\Nfoolishness once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you give birth to a healthy child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that time I couldn't understand what\Nthe director was trying to tell me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't tell us anything\Nabout that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:59.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well give her a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what, but can you\Ntalk to us about something more?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't pay attention to this Ren,\Nit doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It troubled me that he was always\Nexchanging e-mails with somebody.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just got a little curious. That was all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Remi Shinjyo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Age: 27\NHeight: 160 cm\N3 Sizes: 87-59-86
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Blood Type: AB\NWeight: 47 kg\NDpt: Gynecology (Head nurse)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ako Fujisawa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Age: 23\NHeight: 157 cm\N3 Sizes: 88-60-90
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Blood Type: O\NWeight: 47 kg\NDpt: Provisional
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hikaru Kodama
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Age: 21\NHeight: 154 cm\N3 Sizes: 79-55-81
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Blood Type: B\NWeight: 43 kg\NDpt: General Care
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ren Nanase
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Age: 22\NHeight: 158 cm\N3 Sizes: 85-57-87
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Blood Type: AB\NWeight: 45 kg\NDpt: Gynecology
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:18:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm Sensei's tool...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... Sensei really loves me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This has to be some kind of sick joke!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:08.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what I wanted to believe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I waited for him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ryuji Hirasaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The man who trifled with me,\NRyuji Hirasaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The man who tried to rob the\Nlife of the child I carried.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ryuji Hirasaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The man I've hated more than\Nanyone else I've ever met.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ryuji Hirasaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't forgive you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't forgive you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:15.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My revenge and my ambition.\NMy future. My everything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Hirasaka-kun.\NIf I allowed you to live,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}her child's life would be in danger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That, above everything I wanted to avoid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I'm the last one to feel that\Npain, then it's all ok.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Hirasaka-kun, I really did love you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... you weren't serious about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I couldn't forgive you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodbye... Hirasaka-kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Hirasaka-Sensei was\Ntemporarily unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he was able to miraculously\Nhold onto his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Director Jinguji was trying to\Nget even with him then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this point, we can't gain\Nanyone's testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything in regards to this case will\Nprobably disappear into the dark, I fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm, it seems to be doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.52,0:21:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe that the only\Npart of your front which...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is protruding at the\Nmoment is your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.98,0:21:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, there still appears to be no\Nchange of color of your nipples.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Ren, do you feel it even\Nduring examination?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Sensei you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is examination too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you become pregnant, this area\Nchanges color and odor too, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What's this Ren, you\Nappear to be damp...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.97,0:22:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now, if they get turned on when\Ngetting examined by the doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.47,0:22:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then it's the patient\Nthat's the strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.77,0:22:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't say anything,\Nthen I won't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do down here exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright then, lie down on\Nyour side over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'll take another\Nlook at your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our child is alive inside here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:49.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't really believe it to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's our baby, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S... Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei don't tell me you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:57.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it... Stop it please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said it was our baby didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough of this charade! That's\NNaoya's damn kid, isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so cruel... aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we take it out and\Nexamine it more thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.81,0:23:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.02,0:23:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop fucking moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell\Ndo you think you're doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to listen\Nto what I tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may be you Sensei, but the one\Nthing I won't allow is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could a doctor, someone who\Nsaves lives, do this kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And besides, this really is your baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, you're the only one I've been with!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ren, you've really become strong after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.85,0:23:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rather than just a woman, you've turned\Ninto a fully qualified mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just testing you is all.\NSorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.69,0:23:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as Sensei loves me, I don't\Neven mind being his tool.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... I just had to protect\Nthe baby inside me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.75,0:24:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I had to protect\Nmyself no matter what.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.28,0:24:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ren... not you as well...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.49,0:24:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to do this to me as well...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.16,0:24:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is the true form of the\Ncreature called "woman"...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.15,0:25:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.86,0:25:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... I... really loved you, Ryuji Hirasaka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.03,0:25:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.12,0:25:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if her story was really the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.37,0:25:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.46,0:25:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it was just\Nan elaborate fabrication.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.05,0:25:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.88,0:25:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However when you're a detective\Nfor a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.76,0:25:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you get to see this kind of case\Nevery once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.56,0:25:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And every time I do I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.77,0:25:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,people's hearts are just darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.27,0:25:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They have a core\Nthat no one could desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.15,0:25:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're true darkness.
